data.name: OpenFintech
data.description: OpenFintech is a financial analysis library designed for Python developers and financial analysts. It provides powerful tools for conducting both trend following and mean reversion analyses, utilizing financial market data. This project aims to make complex financial algorithms accessible and easy to use.
